BFN 

  [Text] President Hafiz al-Asad has sent a cable to Akbar 
Hashemi-Rafsanjani, president of the Islamic Republic of Iran, 
expressing his condolences over the victims of the criminal 
incident in the city of Mashhad. 
  The following is the text of the cable: We have been 
extremely pained by the falling of victims as a result of the 
criminal incident which occurred in the holy city of Mashhad. 
We strongly denounce this incident and express to your 
excellency and to the families of the victims our heartfelt 
condolences. We pray to God Almighty to grant the injured 
speedy recovery. 

